rows.label: qev060504_MSG0001
rows.name:
Goodness! Those Zaruboggan do have some rather
impressive abilities, don't you think?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060504_MSG0002
rows.name:
Even the latest in in Ma-non tech couldn't clean all that
up, probably?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060504_MSG0003
rows.name:
Argh! At at at this rate, the whole plant is going to go!
And then all of New LA will be in danger, won't it?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060504_MSG0004
rows.name:
Just get out there and recruit, okay, Liza?
I'll take anybody with a pulse, because this this
mess isn't getting cleaned up without a crew![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060504_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, this looks like a catastrophe, doesn't it?
I mean, it's REALLY busted.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev060504_MSG0006
rows.name:
Even a Ma-non engineer wouldn't be able to fix this
without a big crew, would they?[ST:wait ]
